		</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">These are a weaker version of the dune tarantula and are also found in arid climates.  They like to poison their victims with a nasty bite, and they hit hard besides.  Kill these with caution, and try to make sure you have a way to clear the poison when the battle is over, or you may find yourself dead despite your victory.</font></td>
  </tr>
